Features
1.Add new tasks with descriptions, priority levels (Low, Medium, High), and due dates.
2.Edit existing tasks to update their details.
3.Mark tasks as completed with a single click.
4.Delete tasks from the list.
5.Persistent storage in tasks.json to save tasks between sessions.
6.Modern UI with a light purple-to-white gradient background for a mobile app-like aesthetic.
7.Input validation for task descriptions and due dates (YYYY-MM-DD format).
8.Displays tasks in a listbox with their status, priority, and due date.
